Quicksort Cake.

This recipe sorts numbers using the quicksort algorithm.

Ingredients.
3 g pivot flour
6 g left sugar
8 g right butter
10 g middle eggs
1 g salt
2 g pepper
1 g vanilla

Method.
Put pivot flour into the mixing bowl.
Put left sugar into the mixing bowl.
Combine middle eggs into the mixing bowl.
Pour contents of the mixing bowl into the baking dish.

Serves 7.
